reviewText: Giada Valenti has such a beautiful voice for these love songs.  I love having the dvd  at my fingertips to play.

People who have seen concert this should get this DVD. The things that  I like about this are first, the list of songs tells you which ones were featured on the TV special and those that are bonuses and while speaking about bonuses, the next thing I like is the bonus of Giada showing her hometown, her family and her friends to viewers of this DVD.

Thank you for your inquiry. I was a little disapointed in the sound format, the content is excellent, I enjoy it very much along with my neighbour.
  I was a bit surprised to see the total came to $46.19 Canadian.
